description: Circular MIL Spec Tools, Hardware & Accessories sealing gasket,conductive,65sh, bright- size n
info:
VG Circular Connectors
        
        
            Amphenol Air LB Germany VG Circular Connectors operate over a wide temperature range (as low as -65°C and up to +175°C) and are designed for harsh environments. The VG Circular Connectors include the GCB-B series, PT round plug connectors, and the SJT round plug connectors. The GCB-B connectors offer reverse bayonet locking (according to VG95234), high reliability, and are waterproof as well as wear- and vibration-resistant. The PT round plug connectors with bayonet locking are approved as per VG95328, MIL26482 Series I for crimp, solder, single solder, and wire-wrap contacts. An HF-sealed version is also available. Scoop-proof SJT round plug connectors with reverse bayonet locking are approved per VG96912, PAN6433-2, JN 1003.

description: Circular MIL Spec Tools, Hardware & Accessories sealing gasket,conductive,65sh, bright- size n
info:
Electrically Conductive Gaskets
        
        
            Amphenol Air LB Germany Electrically Conductive Gaskets offer a comprehensive range of electrically conductive gaskets for receptacles and accessories. These electrically conductive gaskets range includes all variants from the VG96940-6. The series features fluorosilicone and a homogeneous mixture of conductive materials such as silver-coated aluminum particles (Version A) or nickel-carbon-particles (Version B). Amphenol Air LB Germany Electrically Conductive Gaskets provide maximum protection against moisture, dirt, and are resistant to aggressive fluids such as oil, hydraulic, or kerosene. Typical applications of electrically conductive gaskets include military, aerospace, and industrial applications.

description: Circular MIL Spec Tools, Hardware & Accessories CAP, CPC, SIZE 23 RECP, BLACK
info:
Circular Plastic Connectors (CPC) Protective Caps
        
        
            TE Connectivity's Circular Plastic Connectors (CPC) Protective Caps are designed to fit the existing CPC plugs and receptacles, providing protection from environmental contaminants. These protective caps are disposable, recyclable, and feature up to 80°C temperature resistance. The CPC protective caps are available in orange, red, black, and yellow colors. These protective caps are used in robotics, industrial machinery, instrumentation, power supplies, material handling, and welding equipment.

description: Circular MIL Spec Contacts Micro Miniature Bulk Head Mounted Plug
info:
2M Warrior Grip Push-Pull Connectors
        
        
            Amphenol Aerospace 2M Warrior Grip Push-Pull Connectors combine fast charging, 10A capability, and compatibility to existing Nett Warrior Push-Pull Connectors. Amphenol Aerospace 2M Warrior Grip Push-Pull Connectors offer numerous enhancements to the standard 2M804 design, including a unique mate-force rating for quick disconnect and selectively plated shells for improved conductivity. The Warrior Grip is tailor-made for nearly any soldier-worn application.

description: Circular MIL Spec Connector RNJ Plug 26 NI sz 13 rot N 13-35 insert
info:
RNJ Rack & Panel Cylindrical Connectors
        
        
            Amphenol Socapex RNJ Rack and Panel Cylindrical Connectors connect electrical and optical devices between a moving unit (rack) and a fixed unit (panel) without any coupling/uncoupling device. This function is ensured by a system of moving and fixed units. Amphenol Socapex RNJ Rack and Panel Connectors are derived from the LJT series and meet or exceed MIL-DTL-38999 Series I requirements. The RNJ series is qualified for the requirements of the standard DAT C 5935 x 0005 HE308 21, 25, 26, and 27T models.

description: Circular MIL Spec Connector TV PLUGS - DURMALON
info:
Durmalon & AP93 Heavy Duty Connectors
        
        
            Amphenol Aerospace Durmalon and AP93 Heavy Duty MIL-DTL-22992 Connectors offer a 40A to 100A current range, 120VAC to 480VAC voltage, and 28, 32, 44, and 52 shell sizes. These heavy duty connectors are a part of the Class "L" series and meet the demand for heavy duty and heavy power connectors that are critical for rugged environmental conditions. The Durmalon finish provides protection against 500 hours of dynamic salt spray, while the AP-93 plating exceeds 1000 hour salt spray requirements. Amphenol Aerospace Durmalon AP93 Heavy Duty Connectors feature a rugged, waterproof design and a programmed coupling sequence.
